1. *Srednje* stara osoba je imala problema sa vidom. (A middle-aged person had vision problems.)
2. On je hodao *srednjom* brzinom. (He was walking at a medium speed.)
3. Učenici su upućeni na *srednje* škole. (The students are directed to the middle school.)
4. *Srednje* obrazovanje je obavezno. (Middle education is mandatory.)
5. Ona je držala *srednje* radno mesto. (She held a middle position.)
6. *Srednje* godišnje plaće su povećane. (The average annual wages have been increased.)